{"tid":735880,"cid":36,"subCid":0,"title":"有冇人覺得應該食咗早餐先刷牙","createTime":"2018-07-09T23:55:09.000Z","updateTime":"2018-07-10T03:50:29.000Z","uid":71166,"like":5,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"6a16e0606d8db719967f5a0bad0247c99f6550e9","tid":735880,"uid":71166,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-09T23:55:09.000Z","msg":"刷牙後會有短時間影響味蕾<br />\n令到食物無咁好味<br />\n<br />\n另外早餐後亦會令口腔有食物渣滓<br />\n刷完等如無刷<br />\n<br />\n所以應該早上先用無牙膏刷牙一次<br />\n<br />\n早刷後再用牙膏加牙線刷一次<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/36.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b25e2701eb801a7b1d0cfc72eb1a1537e09a5a06","tid":735880,"uid":35547,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-10T00:00:02.000Z","msg":"唔刷牙先咁你連埋谷左一晚既口臭同污糟野落肚<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a066e88aaff2d8ccfc93cc256c08ca89c3a88cac","tid":735880,"uid":183383,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-10T00:06:33.000Z","msg":"極臭......"},{"pid":"b7b0cde1978d514bd1e81d008eefb626ea3a6e36","tid":735880,"uid":191815,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-10T00:07:43.000Z","msg":"起身從來唔刷<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"31877b8803e577d80bf3688f9763dad9510d4e11","tid":735880,"uid":172297,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-10T00:09:19.000Z","msg":"刷兩次, 唔好懶<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"971c937a8670f4a1307312bb5359fdf5766de204","tid":735880,"uid":130901,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b25e2701eb801a7b1d0cfc72eb1a1537e09a5a06","tid":735880,"uid":35547,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-10T00:00:02.000Z","msg":"唔刷牙先咁你連埋谷左一晚既口臭同污糟野落肚<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-10T00:10:27.000Z","msg":"有說法係應該一早食啖水，吞晒D隔夜渣先"},{"pid":"d131de70da0c28400e25ca02249d112605b834b4","tid":735880,"uid":187363,"like":0,"dislike